headline: LCNB (LCNB) Q4 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: LCNB (LCNB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -9.09% and +5.10%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
